name: Sketch Card Commission
description: Subject of your choice done in full color on 2.5" x 3.5" card stock. The selected images are just examples of my work (check my website for more examples). Your card will be done similar to those pictured featuring a character of your choice. It will be a one of a kind 1/1 original piece of art. Film and television characters preferred, but will do anything with the right reference photo. Thanks!
